akprx (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=low

  * Initial release
  * FastAPI broker daemon on 127.0.0.1:8080
  * Adaptor registry — register, list, show, remove API providers
  * Secret management — add, list, remove, rotate keys (values never exposed)
  * Generic /call proxy — any REST API, any method
  * akprx check — validates service, adaptors, and key pairing
  * Auto-restart service after key add, rotate, remove
  * CLI — akprx status, adaptor, key, call, check, version
  * Debian package with automated postinst setup
  * Locked system user, localhost only, ProtectSystem=full
  * MIT license

 -- Belka <belka0fficial@github.com>  Mon, 06 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0300
